# Configuring IAM Policies on GCP

This lab focuses on identity and access management in GCP. It walks through applying custom IAM roles, simulating permissions, and verifying least-privilege access using service accounts and audit logs.

## Features
- Assigned IAM roles to users and service accounts
- Used `Policy Simulator` to preview effects of role changes
- Audited policy bindings and logs for misconfigurations

## Tools & Technologies
- GCP IAM
- Cloud Console
- gcloud CLI
- Policy Troubleshooter

## Skills Demonstrated
✅ IAM roles & policy design  
✅ Permission simulation & validation  
✅ Audit and security analysis
